INSERT INTO file_watch_consumer_offsets (
            group_name,
            library_id,
            last_event_id,
            last_detected_at,
            updated_at
        ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, NOW())
        ON CONFLICT (group_name, library_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            last_event_id = EXCLUDED.last_event_id,
            last_detected_at = EXCLUDED.last_detected_at,
            updated_at = NOW()
